..TEXT:
|Padre mio, ch$e non m'aiuti?~ An echo of Christ's
words from the Cross (Matt. 27:46): "Eli, eli, lamma sabacthani?
hoc est: Deus meus, Deus meus, ut quid dereliquisti me?"  ("`Eli,
Eli, lema sabacthani,' that is, `My God, my God, why hast thou
forsaken me?'")  In this connection the reader should note the
expression "porre a tal croce" (vs. 87).
